Skull-1 to Delta-1:

1050
01:46:06,282 --> 01:46:07,367
Mission accomplished.

1051
01:46:08,034 --> 01:46:09,369
I'm heading home.

1052
01:46:13,164 --> 01:46:15,250
This is Delta-1: Roger.

1053
01:47:49,678 --> 01:47:51,763
Now the real hardship starts.

1054
01:47:52,931 --> 01:47:58,061
In this galaxy alone, there are supposed to be over a thousand fleets...

1055
01:47:58,061 --> 01:48:01,189
...led by mobile fortresses of Bodolza and the Lapramiz-class.

1056
01:48:01,606 --> 01:48:02,607
Probably.

1057
01:48:03,983 --> 01:48:07,362
But a single song could bring all this change.

1058
